ComicInfo.Title: Yule Be Sorry!
ComicInfo.Summary: The Tick returns in an all-new, continuing comic series! The Tick enjoys the Christmas season with Arthur and his super-hero pals. But among the present is one from a super-villain! Look for this all-new series into 2010 with all-new tales of Tick-ish adventures!
